Magical. A dream. An elegy to our world and a reminder to keep living in it. I wonder many things. Watching this felt healing and kind. The ending was so sudden and essential: and while walking home I recorded a voice memo to someone dear to me that I knew I couldn’t send, so I talked to myself and in doing that I understood why the ending had to be what it is. I’m excited to see this again. The…
